  <brief_title>A Study to Evaluate the Effectiveness and Safety of RXI 109 on the Outcome of Scar Revision Surgery in Healthy Adults</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-Center, Prospective, Randomized, Double-Blind, Within-Subject Controlled, Phase 2a Study to Evaluate the Effectiveness and Safety of RXI 109 on the Outcome of Scar Revision Surgery on Transverse Hypertrophic Scars on the Lower Abdomen Resulting From Previous Surgeries in Healthy Adults</official_title>
